{"tid":1535750,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"急招倉鼠托管（薄酬）","createTime":"2019-09-03T13:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T19:17:57.000Z","uid":53538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c855cdf4e56362e85f5e4e24d0bee8cd30d21de1","tid":1535750,"uid":53538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:01:35.000Z","msg":"事原我要係4/9同鼠鼠睇醫生（時間係10：00）<br />\n因為我11：30有急事 所以無時間接鼠鼠返屋企 而診所唔可以收留鼠鼠<br />\n所以我希望有巴絲可以幫我暫時照顧2-3小時<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下有個小小條件 <br />\n近荃灣區（因為荃灣睇醫生）<br />\n最好有養倉鼠經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係暫照顧2-3個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有意請留tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23923d63b89de1b5113d3492fd00ad83525ef834","tid":1535750,"uid":53538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f119cf4e9cecb8cdb6c008d6f8334bcad214a6a","tid":1535750,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30c12c5540bd3a48049b37fe6a0a40868ebe8188","tid":1535750,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"幫你推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n照顧幾個鐘係咪睇住佢就得？"},{"pid":"b733616a2f3e33a7ea3fc6c07439394fcc62d520","tid":1535750,"uid":53538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30c12c5540bd3a48049b37fe6a0a40868ebe8188","tid":1535750,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"幫你推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n照顧幾個鐘係咪睇住佢就得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"係呀 我會交低少量食物俾佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/